<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-50 font-sans text-gray-800 flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200 py-10 mb-8">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Last updated: February 12, 2026</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="mb-auto">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-8 md:p-12 space-y-10"
        >
          <div>
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
            >
              <span
                class="bg-green-100 text-[#2E7D32] w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm"
                >1</span
              >
              Information We Collect
            </h2>

            <div class="ml-11 space-y-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">
                  1.1 Information You Submit to Us
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  We welcome all visitors to browse our website. If you choose
                  to make a purchase, we collect essential contact information
                  required to process your order—such as your name, address,
                  phone number, email address, and payment details. Optional
                  fields may collect additional information like alternate
                  shipping addresses or special instructions.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">
                  1.2 Information Gathered Automatically
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  Our servers automatically collect standard tracking
                  information, including IP addresses, log files, and browsing
                  activity. This data helps us understand site usage trends and
                  improve user experience. All automatically collected data is
                  aggregated and is not linked to any personally identifiable
                  information.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
            >
              <span
                class="bg-green-100 text-[#2E7D32] w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm"
                >2</span
              >
              Use of Cookies
            </h2>
            <div class="ml-11">
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Cookies help ensure smooth navigation and
                functionality—especially for Shopping Cart operations. Cookies
                may also be used to customize content based on your browsing
                behavior. You may disable cookies in your browser settings;
                however, doing so may affect the website’s functionality.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
            >
              <span
                class="bg-green-100 text-[#2E7D32] w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm"
                >3</span
              >
              How We Use Your Information
            </h2>
            <div class="ml-11">
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Information you provide may be used to process payments, fulfill
                orders, ship products, contact you about your purchase, and
                respond to inquiries. We may also send promotional content with
                your consent.
              </p>
              <div
                class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-[#4CAF50] p-4 text-sm text-gray-600"
              >
                <p>
                  The website is owned by <strong><%= company.name %> Traders</strong>.
                  You may download or print materials solely for personal,
                  non-commercial use. Modification, redistribution,
                  republication, or public display of any material without
                  written permission is strictly prohibited.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
            >
              <span
                class="bg-green-100 text-[#2E7D32] w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm"
                >4</span
              >
              Disclaimer & Limitation of Liability
            </h2>
            <div class="ml-11">
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                 <%= company.name %> Traders is not liable for any direct, indirect,
                incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use or
                inability to use this website. All information, images, pricing,
                options, offers, and content may be changed without notice. If
                you disagree with any terms of this policy, your sole remedy is
                to discontinue using the website.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
            >
              <span
                class="bg-green-100 text-[#2E7D32] w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm"
                >5</span
              >
              Leads From Promotions
            </h2>
            <div class="ml-11">
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Information collected through promotional campaigns may be used
                to communicate product offers and promotional activities. By
                submitting your details, you agree to be contacted for marketing
                purposes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
            >
              <span
                class="bg-green-100 text-[#2E7D32] w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm"
                >6</span
              >
              Sharing of Personal Information
            </h2>
            <div class="ml-11">
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                In the event of a merger, acquisition, restructuring, or
                business transfer, your information may be shared with or sold
                to another entity. The receiving entity will be bound by this
                Privacy Policy.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
            >
              <span
                class="bg-green-100 text-[#2E7D32] w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm"
                >7</span
              >
              Links to Other Websites
            </h2>
            <div class="ml-11">
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Our website may contain links to third-party sites. We are not
                responsible for their content or privacy practices. We encourage
                users to review the privacy policies of these external sites.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
            >
              <span
                class="bg-green-100 text-[#2E7D32] w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm"
                >8</span
              >
              Your Consent
            </h2>
            <div class="ml-11">
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                By using this website and providing your information, you
                consent to the collection and use of your information as
                outlined in this Privacy Policy.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2
              class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
            >
              <span
                class="bg-green-100 text-[#2E7D32] w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm"
                >9</span
              >
              Choice / Opt-Out / Data Deletion
            </h2>
            <div class="ml-11">
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Users may opt out of marketing communications at any time by
                clicking the unsubscribe link in emails or by contacting our
                support team. You may also request deletion of your data from
                our systems.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-4">
                <a
                  href="/contact"
                  class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold hover:underline"
                  >Contact Support Team &rarr;</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="h-20"></div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
